If you’re a chocolate lover with a bit of a bourbon kick, then chocolate bourbon pots de crème are the dessert for you! These creamy, dreamy pots of chocolatey goodness are infused with a generous splash of bourbon, giving them a bold and boozy flavor that is sure to satisfy. The chocolate and bourbon are balanced perfectly, so you won’t feel overwhelmed by the alcohol, but you’ll definitely taste it. And with their rich, velvety texture and indulgent flavour, these pots de crème are guaranteed to become your new go-to indulgence. So why wait? Treat yourself to a little chocolate bourbon heaven today with this recipe by Woodford Reserve. 